posts.post_title: WTT Piedmont 350-460 Factory 42 back for other T206's I need.
posts.post_content:
Posted By: Jim T
I have a piedmont factory 42 back and since I am not a really back collector I would like to trade for other T206's that I need.  I am willing to trade for almost anything: some commons in P-F condition, a low tier HOFer, or maybe I can throw in some cash for a P Cy Young portrait.  Let me know what you have.  I have included a list of cards that I currently have (it's shorter than the list of what I need).

email me with offers athierfelder@wi.rr.com
